    {
      "name": "Exam",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Submit Exam",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (jsonData.data && jsonData.data.submissionId) {",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set(\"submissionId\", jsonData.data.submissionId);",
                  "        console.log(\"‚úÖ Submission ID saved:\", jsonData.data.submissionId);",
                  "    }",
                  "    if (jsonData.data) {",
                  "        console.log(\"üìä Exam Result:\");",
                  "        console.log(\"   Score: \" + jsonData.data.achievedScore + \"/\" + jsonData.data.totalScore);",
                  "        console.log(\"   Percentage: \" + jsonData.data.percentage.toFixed(2) + \"%\");",
                  "        console.log(\"   Status: \" + (jsonData.data.passed ? \"‚úÖ PASSED\" : \"‚ùå FAILED\"));",
                  "        console.log(\"   Correct: \" + jsonData.data.correctAnswers);",
                  "        console.log(\"   Wrong: \" + jsonData.data.wrongAnswers);",
                  "    }",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"userId\": \"{{userId}}\",\n  \"quizId\": \"{{quizId}}\",\n  \"answers\": [\n    {\n      \"questionId\": \"{{questionId}}\",\n      \"answerIds\": [\"{{answerId}}\"]\n    }\n  ]\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/exam/submit",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "exam", "submit"]
            },
            "description": "üìù Submit exam answers and get immediate results\n\n**Request Body:**\n- userId: User taking the exam\n- quizId: Quiz being taken\n- answers: Array of question-answer pairs\n  - questionId: Question ID\n  - answerIds: Array of selected answer IDs\n\n**Response:**\n- Detailed results with score, percentage, pass/fail\n- Individual question results\n- Saves submission to database\n\n**Scoring Logic:**\n- Single Choice: Must select exactly 1 correct answer\n- Multiple Choice: Must select ALL correct answers (no partial credit)\n- Pass threshold: 50%\n\n**Auto-saves:**\n- Submission ID to {{submissionId}}\n- Prints score summary to console\n\n**Example:**\nFor a quiz with 3 questions (scores: 5, 10, 5):\n- Total Score: 20\n- If correct: 2/3 questions\n- Achieved: 15/20 (75%) - PASSED ‚úÖ"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ],
      "description": "Exam submission and grading endpoints"
